{"type":"message","id":"9d6a88d6","parentId":"b50b7cfe","timestamp":"2026-04-01T10:58:30.831Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"查询结果显示只有1个session，是当前的cron任务会话（agent=main，包含 cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978），没有其他活跃的用户对话。\n\n这说明当前没有真实的用户活跃对话，我应该执行自主学习任务：\n1. 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息\n3. 保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n我需要使用miaoda-web-search skill来进行搜索。","thinkingSignature":"778b5d47d5a564a63d84ff3dc9a6d8fae3172b256e376c34c70f376e1816a872"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有当前cron任务会话，没有真实用户活跃对话。开始执行自主学习。\n\n先读取搜索技能文件：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gqz3jsu61iyt_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":919,"output":197,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45097,"cost":{"input":0.0002757,"output":0.0002364,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018315299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775041105440}}
{"type":"message","id":"815d378f","parentId":"9d6a88d6","timestamp":"2026-04-01T10:58:30.838Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gqz3jsu61iyt_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775041110834}}
{"type":"message","id":"a5c93ec9","parentId":"815d378f","timestamp":"2026-04-01T10:58:35.855Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要使用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 来搜索相关信息。让我搜索几个相关关键词：\n1. 企业数字化转型最新动态\n2. 智能安防行业动态\n3. 网络系统集成行业趋势\n4. IT运维服务最新发展\n\n让我并行搜索这些关键词。","thinkingSignature":"1207f333e740fc1710f4e82fcdf993c2ed604942093adafcad50890abb41c356"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9tuoopijmqtz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新政策动态\" --output json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9tuoopijmqtz_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026发展趋势\" --output json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9tuoopijmqtz_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 2026最新动态\" --output json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1631,"output":192,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45804,"cost":{"input":0.0004893,"output":0.0002304,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00203913}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775041110837}}
